[36m(main_task pid=16038)[0m    - Total students = \( 20 \text{ students/class} \times 3 \text{ classes} = 60 \text{ students} \).
[36m(main_task pid=16038)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=16038)[0m 2. **Determine the number of girls in the school:**
[36m(main_task pid=16038)[0m    - The school is 50% boys and 50% girls.
