[36m(main_task pid=16038)[0m    - Number of girls = \( 0.5 \times 60 = 30 \text{ girls} \).
[36m(main_task pid=16038)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=16038)[0m 3. **Determine the number of girls in the first and second classes:**
[36m(main_task pid=16038)[0m    - The first class has 15 girls.
